List available packages in Bioconductor

Source: R/bioc-packages.R
wood_bioc_packages.Rd

This function queries Bioconductor for a list of available packages. Current and previous releases can be queried, up to Bioconductor 1.5.

Usage

wood_bioc_packages(release = "release")

Arguments

release

character(1)
Bioconductor release to query for. Can be either a numeric code (like 3.12) or one of two keywords: "release" and "devel".

Value

A character vector of available packages.

See also

Functions for Bioconductor: wood_bioc_dependencies(), wood_bioc_releases(), wood_bioc_version()

Functions that query available packages: wood_core_packages(), wood_cran_packages(), wood_github_packages(), wood_local_packages(), wood_packages(), wood_runiverse_packages(), wood_url_packages()
